trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Command" name="Command" href=""></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Udostępnia dane dla <xref uid="langword_csharp_Command" name="Command" href=""> </xref> zdarzeń.

trans-unit.source: The `Command` event is raised when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton>, or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> control button in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField> object is clicked.
trans-unit.target: `Command` Zdarzenie jest zgłaszane, gdy <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton>, lub <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>przycisku w <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField>obiekt zostanie kliknięty.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>

trans-unit.source: The DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs class is used internally by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.OnBubbleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField.HandleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName> methods to access information about the event that was raised.
trans-unit.target: Klasa DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs jest używana wewnętrznie przez <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.OnBubbleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField.HandleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metody dostęp do informacji o zdarzeniu, który został zgłoszony.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField.HandleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.OnBubbleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
